de.javakaffee.web.msm
Class MemcachedBackupSession

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.catalina.session.StandardSession
      de.javakaffee.web.msm.MemcachedBackupSession
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.http.HttpSession, org.apache.catalina.Session
public final class MemcachedBackupSession
extends org.apache.catalina.session.StandardSession

The session class used by the MemcachedBackupSessionManager.

This class is needed to e.g.

  • be able to change the session id without the whole notification lifecycle (which includes the application also).
  • provide access to internal fields of the session, for serialization/deserialization
  • be able to coordinate backup and expirationUpdate

setIdForRelocate

protected void setIdForRelocate(java.lang.String id)
Set a new id for this session.
Before setting the new id, it removes itself from the associated manager. After the new id is set, this session adds itself to the session manager.

Parameters:
id - the new session id
